# Development Environment Configuration
# This file documents the development setup for the FreeIntvProjects workspace

## Platform Information
PLATFORM=windows
OS_VERSION=Windows 10/11 (64-bit)
ARCHITECTURE=x86_64

## Compiler Toolchain
COMPILER=MinGW64
COMPILER_PATH=C:\mingw64
GCC_VERSION=15.2.0
MINGW_MAKE=C:\mingw64\bin\mingw32-make.exe

## Build System
BUILD_TOOL=mingw32-make
BUILD_COMMAND=mingw32-make platform=win

## Shell Environment
SHELL=PowerShell
POWERSHELL_VERSION=5.1

## Environment Variables
# Add MinGW64 to PATH for builds:
# $env:PATH += ";C:\mingw64\bin"

## Project Paths
WORKSPACE=c:\Users\Jason\Documents\Visual Studio\FreeIntvProjects
FREEINTVDS_PROJECT=FreeIntvDS
FREEINTV_WORKING_KEYPAD=FreeIntvWorkingKeypad

## Notes for Agents
- This is a Windows-only development environment
- Use PowerShell commands, not Unix/Linux commands
- Use backslashes (\) for paths, not forward slashes
- MinGW64 must be available in PATH for compilation
- File operations should use PowerShell cmdlets (Get-Item, Remove-Item, etc.)
- Commands like 'make', 'head', 'tail' require Unix tools (unavailable by default)
- Use native Windows commands (del, dir, type) or PowerShell equivalents

## Key Commands for This Environment
### Add MinGW to PATH
$env:PATH += ";C:\mingw64\bin"

### Compile FreeIntvWorkingKeypad
cd "c:\Users\Jason\Documents\Visual Studio\FreeIntvProjects\FreeIntvWorkingKeypad"
mingw32-make platform=win

### Clean Build
cd "c:\Users\Jason\Documents\Visual Studio\FreeIntvProjects\FreeIntvWorkingKeypad"
Get-Item -Path src\*.o -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Remove-Item -Force
Get-Item -Path src\deps\*\*.o -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Remove-Item -Force -Recurse
Get-Item -Path *.dll -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Remove-Item -Force

### Git Operations
cd "c:\Users\Jason\Documents\Visual Studio\FreeIntvProjects"
git status
git branch
git add -A
git commit -m "message"
git push origin branch-name

